4. LICENSE TIERS

Signet Stack offers the following standard tiers. All pricing is annual
subscription. Perpetual licenses with annual maintenance are available on
request.

  Starter       — Up to 5 developers, 1 production deployment node.
                  Includes email support (2 business day SLA).

  Professional  — Up to 25 developers, up to 10 production deployment nodes.
                  Includes priority email + video support (1 business day SLA),
                  quarterly dependency and CVE review.

  Enterprise    — Unlimited developers and deployment nodes.
                  Includes dedicated support channel, indemnification clause,
                  custom SLA, SBOM attestation, and audit assistance.

  OEM / ISV     — Redistribution rights: embed Signet Forge in a product
                  shipped to your customers. Pricing based on deployment volume.
                  Requires separate OEM agreement.

Exact pricing, order forms, and contract terms are available directly from
Signet Stack.

